Recommends: gnome-disk-utility, gnome-system-monitor, fonts-noto
Description: Aptura Shell Wayland desktop session
 The distro-owned default desktop: a labwc Wayland session with waybar,
 wofi, swaybg, mako and Aptura session/screenshot/power helpers, plus the
 supporting tray applets, audio stack and portals. SDDM is the display
 manager. Configuration ships in /etc/xdg so users keep the Aptura baseline.
